cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.LO. 

The paper focuses on bug detection in MPI programs, which is a software engineering topic, hence cs.SE is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes an on-the-fly schedule algorithm, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of symbolic execution and coverage analysis is related to data structures (cs.DS) and logic in computer science (cs.LO).
